tag name|||John Wick VR: Chapter 1
tag jj|||John Wick VR: Chapter 1 immerses you into the Continental Hotel, a safe haven and central hub for the world’s most elite assassins. You will not have a gun in this experience, but it is the lead in to a first-person-shooter VR game coming soon from the creators of Payday.  Controls: Press and hold the trigger to pick up an object, release the trigger to drop it, and remember, you can duck in VR.  Disclaimer: Before using, read the health and safety warnings in the VR headset instruction manual. Carefully follow all instructions for setup and use. This experience is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. Review surroundings and clear obstacles before use. Take steps to prevent pets, children, or other obstacles entering or otherwise obstructing the area during use. Some people may experience motion sickness, nausea, disorientation, blurred vision, or other discomfort while viewing virtual reality content. If you experience any of these symptoms, stop using immediately and remove the VR headset. For more serious or ongoing symptoms, you may want to consult a doctor.
